author: Comics Explained
description:
A+X (2012) Issues 17 and 18.

▸ A+X was a Marvel comic book series that ran for 18 issues, featuring two-story issues where an Avenger teamed up with an X-Man for an adventure, inverting the conflict from the Avengers vs. X-Men event.
